- The key market players in the global molded wood pallets market include Brambles Ltd., Millwood, Inc., PGS Group, Rehrig Pacific Company, Schoeller Allibert, Craemer Holding GmbH, and CABKA Group, among others. These companies are actively involved in product development, strategic collaborations, and mergers and acquisitions to strengthen their market position and expand their product offerings in the molded wood pallets segment.

